{"tid":144151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華列一號候選人 八婆二號  胡官三號","createTime":"2017-03-05T07:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T08:52:34.000Z","uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf5856ea6cab8d754d98094d654cfa5d8ea4261","tid":144151,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"選舉管理委員會今日為特首選舉候選人舉行簡介會，向候選人講解進行競選活動時，應注意的事項等，並進行選票排名次序抽籤，特首候選人林鄭月娥、曾俊華及胡國興均有出席簡介會。<br />\n選舉管理委員會主席馮驊法官主持簡介會，廉政公署及香港郵政代表亦有出席。選舉主任朱芬齡以抽籤方式決定候選人在選票上的排名次序，以及分配選舉廣告指定展示位置。結果1至3號的候選人，順序為曾俊華、林鄭月娥及胡國興。 <br />\n<br />\n上次６８９都系一號<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11d477fd1a41ee22025003e6101afb738fdf15e","tid":144151,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:58:35.000Z","msg":"淋病年年考第一，抽到二號會唔會喊?"},{"pid":"e4afeb0748702fe8e15d0676419c705d2c7f5df9","tid":144151,"uid":43072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淋病年年考第一，抽到二號會唔會喊?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a5ace0997e5e89b094b8f74a540115e12217a0","tid":144151,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淋病年年考第一，抽到二號會唔會喊?</blockquote><br />\n５柒夠票攞第一"},{"pid":"ff01d1791b66ce466dd293dba074733fa4cff9ea","tid":144151,"uid":9006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697ec54e4074765f433ae689950bec344f38f114","tid":144151,"uid":66149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">系你老母</span>"},{"pid":"d577478f9f82833e274ff48e1c6f5fef4ae3395b","tid":144151,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T08:52:34.000Z